result.notes: Dataset containing kelp understorey algae abundance and biomass information from dive quadrat surveys. The study was carried out by the Dan Smale Lab at the Marine Biological Association (Plymouth). The purpose of this study was to look at differences in kelp understorey biodiversity at different sites around the UK.
